==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Repullulate
<hw>Re*pul"lu*late</hw> <pr>(r?-p?l"l?-l?t)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>repullulare</ets>, <ets>repullulatum</ets>. See
<er>Pullulate</er>.]</ety> <def>To bud again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Though tares <qex>repullulate</qex>, there is wheat still left in
the field.</q> <rj><qau>Howell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Repullulation</ent>⟦br⟧
